{"id":"811923666089771008","type":"text","timestamp":1774310747,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811923666089771008","is_reblog":true,"added_content":true,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://seraphina-aureline.tumblr.com/post/811921242658635776/me-when-a-cute-girl-says-hi\">seraphina-aureline</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811889627786100736\">goodtransgirl</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811887495929331712\">goodtransgirl</a>:</p><blockquote><p>~me playing Leaf Green~</p><p>&ldquo;X is immobilized by love!&rdquo;</p><p>Come on Pokemon, don&rsquo;t you know that the proper response if they&rsquo;re both girls is: </p><p>&ldquo;X is too gay to function!&rdquo;</p></blockquote><p>Had to do it&hellip;</p><figure data-orig-height=\"190\" data-orig-width=\"256\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cf3f01722137388255d2eaf3de4229bd/3783d97217e57c2f-c6/s640x960/ea579c534452681540f24485a3877c584d867778.png\" data-orig-height=\"190\" data-orig-width=\"256\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cf3f01722137388255d2eaf3de4229bd/3783d97217e57c2f-c6/s75x75_c1/c7f5298a3b51f3540b153d1ec0b312263b103d98.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cf3f01722137388255d2eaf3de4229bd/3783d97217e57c2f-c6/s100x200/6455f03563f207b2e98fe3737","reblog_comment":"<p>Hi! </p>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"goodtransgirl"},"post":{"id":"811887495929331712"},"content_raw":"<p>~me playing Leaf Green~</p><p>“X is immobilized by love!”</p><p>Come on Pokemon, don’t you know that the proper response if they’re both girls is: </p><p>“X is too gay to function!”</p>"},{"blog":{"name":"goodtransgirl"},"post":{"id":"811889627786100736"},"content_raw":"<p><p>Had to do it…</p><figure data-orig-height=\"190\" data-orig-width=\"256\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cf3f01722137388255d2eaf3de4229bd/3783d9